<paragraph blockId="7.[264,1323,1201,1870]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[264,436,1201,1227]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">Body (male):</emphasis>
Length: 
<quantity box="[562,716,1202,1228]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.6" metricValueMax="3.7" metricValueMin="3.5" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="3.6" valueMax="3.7" valueMin="3.5">3.5–3.7 mm</quantity>
; pronotal width: 
<quantity box="[945,1128,1202,1228]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.95" metricValueMax="8.1" metricValueMin="7.8" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="0.795" valueMax="0.81" valueMin="0.78">0.78–0.81 mm</quantity>
; crown length: 
<quantity box="[264,444,1242,1268]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.55" metricValueMax="2.9" metricValueMin="2.2" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="0.255" valueMax="0.29" valueMin="0.22">0.22–0.29 mm</quantity>
; crown production: 
<quantity box="[697,877,1242,1268]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.15" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="0.115" valueMax="0.13" valueMin="0.1">0.10–0.13 mm</quantity>
; crown production ratio: 
<number box="[1197,1318,1242,1268]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="0.42000000000000004" valueMax="0.46" valueMin="0.38">0.38–0.46</number>
; interocular width: 
<quantity box="[500,684,1282,1308]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.9" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.8" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="0.39" valueMax="0.4" valueMin="0.38">0.38–0.40 mm</quantity>
; face length: 
<quantity box="[871,1055,1282,1308]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.25" metricValueMax="9.5" metricValueMin="9.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="0.925" valueMax="0.95" valueMin="0.9">0.90–0.95 mm</quantity>
; interantennal width: 
<quantity box="[264,439,1322,1348]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.3999999999999995" metricValueMax="3.5" metricValueMin="3.3" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" unit="mm" value="0.33999999999999997" valueMax="0.35" valueMin="0.33">0.33–0.35 mm</quantity>
. Dried specimens yellow or yellow­gold with cream markings. Forewings greenish yellow and subhyaline in basal 
<number box="[744,760,1362,1388]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="2.0">2</number>
/ 
<number box="[770,784,1362,1388]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="3.0">3</number>
, hyaline or dusky hyaline in apical 
<number box="[1206,1217,1362,1388]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number box="[1229,1245,1362,1388]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="3.0">3</number>
, some specimens with diffuse dusky spot on commissural margin near apex of claval sutre; third apical cell stalked (
<number box="[496,511,1444,1470]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="3.0">3</number>
rd and 
<number box="[584,599,1444,1470]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" value="4.0">4</number>
th apical veins fused basally) arising from cell R. 
<collectingCountry box="[1185,1244,1444,1470]" name="India" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">Hind</collectingCountry>
wings characteristic of genus.
</paragraph>
